narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I developed new patience for seeing a large project all the way through and understand of what I see as unique aspects of my compositional voice.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: All strengths - it is great that senior are allowed free reign compositionally to put together ambitious projects and my advising has been great.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Of course all music majors should do senior composition projects!
